			<div class="comment-content"><p>I like ceramic vs. the smooth steel because it actually removes a little amount of metal each time you use it, creating a fresh apex instead of just bending it back and forth like a smooth steel does. The key is to use it alternating strokes w/ very light pressure until your edge is sharp again. Thanks!</p>
